      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Muddy Revival",
        "Client": "Dame Rondine",
        "Description": "As I don\u0027t have to hide my identity\r\nany longer, I would very much like\r\nto get back in shape. I fear that\r\nmy skills might have dulled during\r\nmy time as a trader. But worry not,\r\nI will still wield my weapon with all\r\nmy might! Come now, let us depart!",
        "Target": "Hunt an Almudron",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Une reprise boueuse",
        "Client": "Dame Rondine",
        "Description": "Vu que je n\u0027ai plus \u00E0 cacher\r\nmon identit\u00E9, je veux chasser\r\n\u00E0 nouveau. Que dirais-tu de\r\nm\u0027aider ? Tu as du talent,\r\nmais je suis un chevalier du\r\nRoyaume. Je suis s\u00FBre de\r\npouvoir t\u0027\u00EAtre utile !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Un ritorno fangoso",
        "Client": "Dama Rondine",
        "Description": "Ora che non devo pi\u00F9 celare la\r\nmia identit\u00E0, voglio tornare a\r\ncacciare. Posso chiederti di\r\naccompagnarmi? So che sei un\r\nasso della caccia, ma anch\u0027io\r\nsono un\u0027abile cavaliera. Potr\u00F2\r\nrendermi utile.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Eine schlammige Wiederbelebung",
        "Client": "Rondine",
        "Description": "Da ich meine Identit\u00E4t nicht mehr\r\nverbergen muss, w\u00FCrde ich sehr\r\ngerne wieder in Form kommen.\r\nIch bef\u00FCrchte, dass meine F\u00E4hig-\r\nkeiten w\u00E4hrend meiner Zeit als\r\nH\u00E4ndlerin gelitten haben. Aber\r\nkeine Sorge, ich werde mithalten!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Almudron.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Regreso embarrado",
        "Client": "Rondine",
        "Description": "Ahora que no necesito ocultar\r\nmi identidad, quiero volver a\r\nponerme en forma. He pasado\r\ndemasiado tiempo en guisa de\r\ncomerciante. Pero no te agobies,\r\n\u00A1a\u00FAn blando mi arma con poder\u00EDo!\r\nVenga, \u00A1pong\u00E1monos en camino!",
        "Target": "Caza un Almudron",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u043D\u043E\u0432\u0430 \u043D\u0430 \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0443",
        "Client": "\u0420\u044B\u0446\u0430\u0440\u044C \u0420\u043E\u043D\u0434\u0438\u043D\u0430",
        "Description": "\u0422\u0430\u043A \u043A\u0430\u043A \u043C\u043D\u0435 \u0431\u043E\u043B\u044C\u0448\u0435 \u043D\u0435 \u043D\u0443\u0436\u043D\u043E\r\n\u0441\u043A\u0440\u044B\u0432\u0430\u0442\u044C \u0441\u0432\u043E\u044E \u043B\u0438\u0447\u043D\u043E\u0441\u0442\u044C, \u044F \u0445\u043E\u0447\u0443\r\n\u0441\u043D\u043E\u0432\u0430 \u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u043D\u0430 \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0443. \u0411\u0443\u0434\u0435\u043C\r\n\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u0432\u043C\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0435? \u0417\u043D\u0430\u044E, \u0442\u044B\r\n\u003CLSNR {\u0441\u0438\u043B\u044C\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u043D\u0438\u043A} {\u0441\u0438\u043B\u044C\u043D\u0430\u044F \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u043D\u0438\u0446\u0430}\u003E, \u043D\u043E \u044F \u0432\u0435\u0440\u043D\u044B\u0439\r\n\u0440\u044B\u0446\u0430\u0440\u044C \u041A\u043E\u0440\u043E\u043B\u0435\u0432\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0430.\r\n\u042F \u0442\u0435\u0431\u0435 \u043F\u0440\u0438\u0433\u043E\u0436\u0443\u0441\u044C!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0410\u043B\u043C\u0443\u0434\u0440\u043E\u043D\u0430",
